{"tid":1444660,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今門發夢係前線嘅同我入一入黎","createTime":"2019-08-11T13:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T13:48:40.000Z","uid":124318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7156c47f1e6b6f543f2cb5a8accd613e7e886da0","tid":1444660,"uid":124318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:00:45.000Z","msg":"借朋友AC一用<br />\n<br />\n我想講﹐今日發夢睇到尖咀單野我嬲撚到屌哂老母。你地守得嘅唔該反擊。阻下速龍推都好。成班守得黎又淆嘅唔該同我玩番快閃﹐如果唔係就同何式凝一撚樣送頭。我明去到依個時候大家都好撚迷唔知想點﹐但頭真係唔係咁送﹐我寧願你去北角打撚柒班紅衫佬。"},{"pid":"4581c78b5d99ab6993d950de01503b7e5301fb6b","tid":1444660,"uid":124318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:19:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de640e36c372b49d9b2f8c412b96d625f1d504ed","tid":1444660,"uid":124318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:19:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af87295d25085331968cea12b43058789ace9d6b","tid":1444660,"uid":124318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:19:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8331ba45f1b1c904abf3c7b56dd3ad207216119","tid":1444660,"uid":124318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:19:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7307a892fa620ace0ff919e9618b7d208b81eab","tid":1444660,"uid":124318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:20:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff47bd568d4311a06c11ed068537b60f2f308bc6","tid":1444660,"uid":257157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:22:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4216aaba03f6719b0bef6375d66165e90f002b8e","tid":1444660,"uid":4298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:25:43.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n岩呀 好多人又要上前幫手 但係又唔知想點咁"},{"pid":"26e82fe4f5c72389299b6ae8928afda9a34d7393","tid":1444660,"uid":124318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:39:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05ca83ebc6e5f502653c7851dab68e2e618e6638","tid":1444660,"uid":124318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score